      "content": "existing as a start... i don't know. i've been \"existing\" for months now and i'm just so tired. it feels like i'm just a ghost haunted by a life that ended. sometimes i look at him and think how much simpler it would be if i didn't have to fight this every single second. if i could just... stop the struggle. it feels like the only way to actually find peace is to just let go of everything.",
